examples.en: You'll get a spanking when your father comes home.

examples.en: If you don't stop that noise, you'll get a spanking!

examples.en: He gave the brat a good spanking.
He keeps his apartment spanking clean.

examples.en: They started walking at a spanking rate.

examples.en: The bathroom tiles were spanking white when she finished cleaning them.
